        Garden Preparation Before Selling: What Actually Pays Off in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The garden is the first thing buyers see and often the last thing sellers prepare. A handful of targeted jobs can add thousands to your result. Most of the rest is wasted money.
      </p>
